// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1109 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a2190888-9d5f-53d8-a5da-52023635cb86

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:3.0*")
